title: Episode 293 w/ Murda Count Harlem

description:
N.O.R.E. & DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode we chop it up with six time platinum recording rapper, Murda Count Harlem! 

Straight outta Harlem, Murda Count joins the Champs for a hilarious episode that you don’t want to miss!

On December 20th, be sure to watch “Miracles Across 125th Street” starring Nick Cannon, Jim Jones, Murda Count Harlem and more! 

Make some noise!!!💐💐💐🏆🏆🏆
